++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Edge_shape_feature_mim.radius_edge_feature_shape_constraint">
The <b>radius_edge_feature_shape_constraint</b> rule constrains the items of a
<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> when it is a radius edge feature shape.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Edge_shape_feature_mim.radius_edge_feature_shape_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> whose name = 'radius edge feature shape' shall have 
one items that is a <express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.length_measure_with_unit"/>.name = 'maximum radius length'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Edge_shape_feature_mim.radius_edge_feature_shape_constraint.wr:WR2">
Each <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> whose name = 'radius edge feature shape' shall have 
one items that is a <express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.length_measure_with_unit"/>.name = 'minimum radius length'.
</ext_description>

