++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Edge_shape_feature_mim.step_edge_feature_shape_constraint">
The <b>step_edge_feature_shape_constraint</b> rule constrains the items of a
<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> when it is a step edge feature shape.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Edge_shape_feature_mim.step_edge_feature_shape_constraint.wr:WR1">
A <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> whose name = 'step edge feature shape' shall have 
exactly one items which is a <express_ref linkend="measure_schema:ir_express:measure_schema.length_measure_with_unit"/> whose name = 
'maximum step depth'.
